ygData.messageBody:
I mentioned these two items earlier on the list.. incase you missed it: I dont know what the power source is for, but force modules are usually items that have a few charges of a dmg spell... at least the ones ive come accrost have. Possible some other types of spells too, but ive only seen dmg spells. As for the power source, i dunno. I came accrost the power source in Sol A at the gnome castle thing, but force modules ive found off loot..

Wes Lobdell,
